# Root-only toolchain registration for the Rust codegen path.
#
# These are here, NOT in MODULE.bazel's register_toolchains(), on purpose:
# register_toolchains() in MODULE.bazel propagates to every downstream consumer,
# which would force rules_rust + a Rust toolchain into Go-only consumers of
# openapi_go_client. .bazelrc is not propagated, so registering here keeps the
# Rust path fully functional for this repo's own tests + examples while leaving
# Go-only consumers' module graphs Rust-free. Consumers of the Rust rules
# register these themselves (see docs/rust_defs.md).
common --extra_toolchains=@rust_toolchains//:all
common --extra_toolchains=//rust:default_rust_client_codegen_toolchain
